org.mellowtech.core.bytestorable

Class CBBitSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mellowtech.core.bytestorable.BStorableImp<BitSet,CBBitSet>
      • org.mellowtech.core.bytestorable.CBBitSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BStorable<BitSet,CBBitSet>

    public class CBBitSet
extends BStorableImp<BitSet,CBBitSet>
    CBBitSet is a BitSet that is suitable for file storage since it extends ByteStorable. This bitSet is wrapper for an ordinary java.util.BitSet.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    rickard.coster@asimus.se, msvens@gmail.com
